Extreme detailed W-sitting pose, (anatomically correct legs:1.2), (internal rotation of thighs:1.3), sitting directly on floor rug, buttocks firmly touching the ground, knees pressed together pointing directly forward toward camera, (shins and feet flared out to sides away from body:1.4), creating a clear symmetric 'W' shape from front view, feet pointing backwards, (full lower body visible:1.1), continuous black sheer pantyhose from skirt hem to toes, no skin gaps, high-denier nylon texture, photorealistic, 8k, high quality.

